you know any one with a aa reset has animation canceling right? {{champion:122}} ,{{champion:36}} {{champion:86}} {{champion:15}} {{champion:254}} {{champion:62}}{{champion:82}} .  Some champions have the ability to animation cancel their auto attacks. {{champion:122}}  Some champs can animation cancel with flash. {{champion:64}} {{champion:201}} {{champion:254}} {{champion:98}} 

I am pretty positive their are more but those are the ones I know of.

I would argue that it isn't really a glitch but more of something that was intended but eventually became a game mechanic.
